snippet: The American teenager finished with a 64 to join the South Korean Se Ri Pak at the top of the leader board in Round 2.
abstract: American teenager Lexi Thompson is tied with South Korean Se Ri Pak atop leader board following second round of the Kraft Nabisco Championship in Rancho Mirage, Calif; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: The American teenager finished with a 64 to join the South Korean Se Ri Pak at the top of the leader board in Round 2.

headline.main: Thompson Finds Putting Touch and Surges Into Tie at Kraft
headline.print_headline: Thompson Forges Tie for Kraft Nabisco Lead
